OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FThe war in the Middle East is having a
OL,7,Fcrippling impact on economies
OL,8,Fthousands of miles away, with the
OL,9,FPhilippines declaring an energy
OL,10,Femergency, ITV News Asia Correspondent
OL,11,FDebi Edward reports
OL,13,FAdditional reporting by Sanjay Jha and
OL,14,FAli Kaifee
OL,16,FA war thousands of miles away has put
OL,17,Fthe Philippines in peril, and so today
OL,18,Fdrivers, students, shop workers, all
OL,19,Ftook to the streets protesting, for
OL,20,Fmore help from their government and
OL,21,Ffor an end to the conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
