OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FThe president has already declared an
OL,7,Fenergy emergency, more than 90% of the
OL,8,Fcountry's fuel come from the Gulf
OL,9,Fregion, so diesel prices in particular
OL,10,Fhave skyrocketed.
OL,12,FA four-day workweek has been imposed,
OL,13,Fand coal production has been ramped up
OL,14,Fto stabilise the grid.
OL,16,FCebu Air, the country's leading budget
OL,17,Fairline has grounded some of its
OL,18,Ffleet, and this import dependent
OL,19,Fnation is braced for food prices and
OL,20,Favailability to impact next.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
