OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FOne public transport driver we spoke
OL,7,Fto said he used to earn one thousand
OL,8,Fpesos a day, yesterday he earned just
OL,9,F150.
OL,11,FAs a single parent, he's worried about
OL,12,Fhow he'll afford his rent, water, food
OL,13,Fand electricity. He's already had to
OL,14,Ftake his child out of school for the
OL,15,Ftime being.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
