OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FAt a gas market on the outskirts of
OL,7,FDelhi, we filmed people who had been
OL,8,Fwaiting days to get a new cylinder.
OL,9,FMany have been camping out at the
OL,10,Fdistribution point, hoping to improve
OL,11,Ftheir chances of getting some fuel.
OL,13,FIn India, like many parts of Asia,
OL,14,Fliquified petroleum gas, or LPG, is
OL,15,Fessential for cooking and most of its
OL,16,Fsupply came from the Middle East. The
OL,17,Fcountry only had a stock of around
OL,18,Fthree-weeks of gas at the start of the
OL,19,Fwar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
