OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FThe fuel shortages have forced several
OL,7,Ffactories in Gujarat's famous ceramics
OL,8,Fcity to shutter.
OL,10,FHundreds of thousands of migrant
OL,11,Fworkers have been told to leave,
OL,12,Fwithout pay and lucrative orders have
OL,13,Fbeen left stuck in warehouses, unable
OL,14,Fto be shipped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
