OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FAs they are in the Philippines
OL,7,Fremittances are a major pillar of the
OL,8,FIndian economy. India is the biggest
OL,9,Fprovider of foreign workers in the
OL,10,FGulf, with more than nine million
OL,11,Fexpats living there, many working in
OL,12,Fthe energy industry.
OL,14,FNeighbouring Pakistan's already
OL,15,Ffragile economy has also been hit hard
OL,16,Fby the soaring energy costs. It is
OL,17,Falmost entirely dependent on the Gulf
OL,18,Ffor its fuel. Supplies are either
OL,19,Frunning out or only a few can afford
OL,20,Fwhat 's left.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
