OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FWe spoke to Samana Riaz who is having
OL,7,Fto turn away business for her food
OL,8,Fdelivery service.
OL,10,FShe said the situation is getting
OL,11,Fworse by the day and she's worried not
OL,12,Fonly is she going to lose her business
OL,13,Fbut not even have fuel to cook for her
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
