OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FOn March 10, the government in
OL,7,FPakistan ordered schools and
OL,8,Funiversities to shut and in some cases
OL,9,Fmove to online learning, to reduce
OL,10,Ffuel consumption, a move which has
OL,11,Faffected approximately forty million
OL,12,Fstudents.
OL,14,FA four-day working week was introduced
OL,15,Ffor civil servants, for the same
OL,16,Freason.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
