OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FThis week Beijing has been shrouded in
OL,7,Fsmog, a reminder of China's continued
OL,8,Fdependence on fossil fuels. Coal is
OL,9,Fstill relied on when oil, gas and
OL,10,Frenewables can't meet the country's
OL,11,Fmassive energy needs.
OL,13,FFor the first time since 2013, the
OL,14,FChinese government has introduced
OL,15,Fprice stabilisation measures for
OL,16,Fdiesel and petrol to try to mitigate
OL,17,Fthe burden paid by consumers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
