OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FChina has long been the biggest
OL,7,Fpurchaser of oil and gas from Iran and
OL,8,FGulf nations. Independent Chinese
OL,9,Frefiners, known as teapots, are the
OL,10,Fworld's largest consumers of US
OL,11,Fsanctioned oil from Iran, Russia and
OL,12,FVenezuela.
OL,14,FThe world's second largest economy has
OL,15,Fenough buffers to weather this
OL,16,Feconomic storm, but its export
OL,17,Findustry is starting to suffer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
