OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FShipping costs, the lack of raw
OL,7,Fmaterials and deferred sales to the
OL,8,FMiddle East are hurting the commodity
OL,9,Findustry among others.
OL,11,FChinese vessels have been among the
OL,12,Ffew given safe passage through the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz, but Beijing can also
OL,14,Fturn to Russia, now its main oil
OL,15,Fsupplier.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
