OL,3,CHow the Iran conflict is taking its
OL,4,Ctoll across Asia
OL,6,FLast year Trumps tariffs threatened
OL,7,FChina's economic growth, this year it
OL,8,Fis the US-led war in Iran. Donald
OL,9,FTrump was due to arrive in Beijing
OL,10,Fnext week for a state visit to
OL,11,Fstabilise relations and steady the
OL,12,Fmarkets.
OL,14,FAccording to the White House, that
OL,15,Fmeeting will now take place mid-May,
OL,16,Fthe US-side apparently believing the
OL,17,FMiddle East conflict, if not its
OL,18,Fconsequences, will be over by then.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
